Syntax: DRAG <character> <direction>

Using this command, attempts to drag a player or mobile out of the room
you are in and into the next room in the direction you choose.  When you
drag someone to another room, if successful, you will also go with them in
the same direction, placing you both in the next room together.  However,
both you and the character your attempting to drag, must both be in a
standing position for this command to work at all.  
~

0 PUSH~
Syntax: PUSH <character> <direction>

Using this command, attempts to push a player or mobile out of the room
you are in, in the direction you choose to push them in.  If successful, the
character will be forced to go in that direction against their will. 
However, the character MUST be in a standing position for this command to
succeed at all.  
~

