102 MPCOMMANDS~
------------------------New Commands Of Interest-----------------------------

1. GENERAL COMMANDS

Syntax: SURRENDER
{x    This command can be issued in combat. If the one giving the command
{x    is a PC and the opponent is a NPC, the NPC will be checked for
{x    a surrender trigger. If the trigger activates, the fight will be
{x    terminated. Otherwise the combat will resume normally. Note that
{x    the mobile can resume the combat in the MOBprogram (see MOB KILL).
{X    If anyone (PC or NPC) surrenders to a PC, the combat will terminate.
{x    The PC can resume the combat with 'kill' command.
{x    With this command, and the use of surrender trigger, non-lethal
{x    combat can be implemented (arenas etc.).

