        c fireseed

Calling apon the elemental forces of fire, a druid can imbue an acorn
with its burning fires.  If a target is specified at the time of casting,
the druid will hurl the fiery acorn at them and it will explode on
contact.  If self or no target is specified the druid will drop the firey
