1 'REPAIR SHIELD' 'CHAIN REPAIR' 'PLATE REPAIR' 'WEAPON REPAIR' 'MEND'~
There are several different Repairing type skills for the Blacksmith to
use, all of which require the smith to be wielding a Blacksmithing Hammer,
and holding an Anvil.  With every skill, the Raw Material used to repair the
object must be the same that the object was made of, i.e. a Shield, made
of Steel, can only be repaired using Steel Material.  Not cash, but Steel
Material. Here are the following skills::
 
Leather Repair: leather <object> <raw material> - Repairs Leather armor
Repair Shield: repair <object> <raw material> - Repairs shields
Chain Repair: chain <object> <raw material> - Repairs Chain armor
Plate Repair: plate <object> <raw material> - Repairs Plate armor
Weapon Repair: weapon <object> <raw material> - Repairs Weapons
Mend: mend <object> <raw material> - Repairs any armor or weapon.
~

