102 'SGIVE'~
Syntax: sgive <item> <player> This command, will give an object in your
inventory, to any player in the MUD.  It will not notify them, or anyone
else in the room that they recieved the item.  It will, however, tell you
that the item was given successfully.  This should prove quite useful for us
Immortals who wish to stay more invisible to the mortals, and wish to give
something to them without them seeing it.  This command does NOT check for
item/weight restrictions on the player who you are giving the object to, so
