0 'PRAY'~
Syntax: 'pray <text>'

This will send a prayer to all the Immortals that are on in the game.
Every Immortal can hear your prayers, and all your prayers are SAVED, so
even if there is no Immortal on, send a Prayer, and you will most likely get
help, as every Immortal can Read the Saved Prayers.  This channel, can be
