possible.  This will aid us in fixing the problem/helping you more
effiencetly.  Now, if you are simply PRAYing for Guidance, ie, Paladine,
lend me the patience to get through these times...  Then go ahead, that is
IC.  Hopefully this makes things clear for you...  
