Holy Order located in Solanthus.  Also check your hometown, for there might be
a group stationed there.
~

1 'TETHER' 'UNTETHER'~
Syntax: tether <victim>
Syntax: untether <victim>

Tether will allow you to tie your pet/mount up, so it won't follow you. 
While tethered, your pet will not follow you when you leave the room, and it
will also not follow you through any gate-like spell, recall, or come to you
if you use HEEL.  To retrieve your pet, you must travel back to the location
to which you tethered it, and Untether it, which will allow your pet to
follow you like normal again.  
~

1 'MERCENARY CLAN'~
{X                        Mercenaries of Ansalon

From all across Ansalon they come. In all shapes and sizes as well.
Warriors, strong and fierce, mages, trained in the art of battle magic.
Some come for the chance to earn cold, hard steel, others seeking
glory, fame and honour while still others, for the love of the kill.
All who can hold their own are welcome to the Mercenary lifestyle.

They are an army without a nation, fighting against whoever they
are paid to, for the most part, taking the side of whoever will pay
