1 KNOCK~
Syntax: c 'knock' <direction>
 
This spell allows the caster to unlock doors or objects which are locked and
would normally require a key to open (and the caster does not happen to have
the key). It works similar to PICK LOCK skill for thieves.
~

1 'ILLUSIONIST'~
Illusionists are mages who have specialized their study in the related
schools of illusion.  As masters of illusion, phantasm, and illusory
alteration, these mages are known to shatter the laws which bind the
